'''Kûng-chhàng-ho̍k''' he en chhái-yung [[Khô-ho̍k]] lâu [[Kî-su̍t]] ke ngièn-lî lòi kié-kiet [[Ngìn-lui]] mun-thì. Kûng-chhàng-sṳ̂ thûng-ko sióng-siong, phan-ton lâu chhûi-lî, chiong khô-ho̍k, kî-su̍t, [[Sṳ-ho̍k]] khi̍p sṳ̍t-chhien kîn-ngiam yin-yung to sat-kie, chṳ-chho, tui-siong fe̍t-he chhàng-si ke chhâu-chok chûng.

Kûng-chhàng-sṳ̂ chui thu̍k-chhu ke ngim-vu he fat-hien, lî-kié pin kiet-ha̍p sṳ̍t-chi ke khiu̍k-han lòi tha̍t-to mân-yi ke kiet-kó. Chṳ̂n-tô chhìn-khóng hâ, sán-phín só-sî fù-ha̍p kî-su̍t yêu-khiù, khì-thâ thiàu-khien ya-he pit-sî mân-chiuk. Liá-chúng thiàu-khien pâu-koat chhòi-liau lòi-ngièn, [[Vu̍t-lî]] fe̍t-he kî-su̍t ke khiu̍k-han, vi-lòi kói-chin ke khó-hàng-sin lâu khì-thâ yîn-su chhiong khó sên-sán-sin khi̍p sṳt-yung-sin.

